This was a collaboration by my fabulous friend mlister and me.

We had gone through several transitions with the article from a nuclear submarine fish to the theatre to keeping the theatre but cutting out a gore-ridden script to refactoring that script into a more whimsical, modern script in order to buckle down on the anachronistic nature of the construct. Finished and topped off by mlister's end log to help contextualize the sights and purpose of the construct, with copious edits.

Thank you to all who have read it!





